snippet.title: Cosmic Collapse - Time to tidy up the solar system, can't have all these planets laying around!
snippet.description:
Purchase on itch.io https://johanpeitz.itch.io/cosmic-collapse?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt It is time to tidy up the solar system. Can't have all these planets laying around!

    Shove planets into each other to make bigger planets
    No stress, take your time
    Like Suika Game but more forgiving and extra features
    Play strategically to trigger insane combos
    Earn missiles to get out of tricky situations
    Totally accurate simulation of celestial bodies

➡️ More from Johan Peitz https://johanpeitz.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
